{"tid":480561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"秀茂坪依個地方真係好撚癲","createTime":"2017-11-26T09:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T10:28:59.000Z","uid":80541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a16f89d2477f63222a5923f78c119718c75013e","tid":480561,"uid":80541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"住咗好多精神有問題嘅人，嫖賭毒咩都齊，試諗下之前有幾單強姦、風化案，啲罪犯唔係住喺寶達就係秀茂坪，每晚喺商場出面都會有為數唔少嘅道友喺度打緊針，有啲人會喺度自言自語，凌晨自己一個女仔返屋企都咪話唔驚。又有好多有手有腳有能力又攞綜援嘅新移民，喺內地唔知有幾多層樓收緊租。有好多喺巴士會大大聲玩cast crush、播電台嘅廢中廢老。衛生環境好差，地方好污糟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位巴絲打又點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d45d7305df8839c0c696c41098bea57450cd3f9","tid":480561,"uid":29835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"依家有班人凌晨會喺商場下面擺檔"},{"pid":"1fb7e1df63c302fece403553b0f3951d56ad42a0","tid":480561,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家有班人凌晨會喺商場下面擺檔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n商場門口有4-5條友擺檔<br />\n係咁叫啲人幫襯佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099d0c4c54cc77309b24014f88f868d12b3d3938","tid":480561,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"有冇mk 妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733fae36b75a17ab39e0e5c93feb36cacb51eaac","tid":480561,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"以前d徙置區未拆<br />\n成地都係道友，一個個叉完電瞓喺樓梯，好撚恐怖"}]}